arrangement.p: Arranged numerically by Volume Number and further arranged chronologically.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Open for scholarly research. Brittle or damaged items are available at the discretion of RAC.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Contains print published versions of the Journal of Experimental Medicine, 1969, 1971-2009.
The series is not fully comprehensive, as Volumes 131, 132, and 137 are not in the archive.
